			"collapsedData":{
				"nodes":[
					{"id":"roadmap_phase5","type":"text","text":"### Phase 5\n**高级特性 (可选)**\n\n- [ ] Istio 服务网格\n- [ ] 全链路灰度\n- [ ] Argo Rollouts\n- [ ] SLO/SLI 监控\n\n**产出:**\n生产级渐进交付能力","x":1700,"y":100,"width":350,"height":280,"color":"6"},
					{"id":"roadmap_timeline","type":"text","text":"### ⏱️ 时间线: `Phase 1 (2w)` → `Phase 2 (3w)` → `Phase 3 (2w)` → `Phase 4 (2w)` → `Phase 5 (Optional)`  **总计: 9-11周**","x":100,"y":420,"width":2550,"height":80,"color":"2"},
					{"id":"roadmap_phase4","type":"text","text":"### Phase 4\n**质量门禁 (2周)**\n\n- [ ] Staging 自动化测试\n- [ ] Kargo 晋升策略\n- [ ] ArgoCD 分析\n- [ ] 回滚 SOP\n\n**产出:**\n可靠的环境晋升流程","x":1300,"y":100,"width":350,"height":280,"color":"2"},
					{"id":"roadmap_phase3","type":"text","text":"### Phase 3\n**聚合系统 (2周)**\n\n- [ ] platform-releases\n- [ ] Aggregator 脚本\n- [ ] 聚合 Changelog\n- [ ] 通知渠道接入\n\n**产出:**\n老板可看的变更汇总","x":900,"y":100,"width":350,"height":280,"color":"5"},
					{"id":"roadmap_phase2","type":"text","text":"### Phase 2\n**需求管理 (2-3周)**\n\n- [ ] Linear 部署配置\n- [ ] GitLab 集成\n- [ ] 团队培训\n- [ ] 状态自动流转\n\n**产出:**\n需求与代码双向链接","x":500,"y":100,"width":350,"height":280,"color":"4"},
					{"id":"roadmap_phase1","type":"text","text":"### Phase 1\n**基础规范 (1-2周)**\n\n- [ ] Conventional Commits\n- [ ] commitlint 配置\n- [ ] 自动 Changelog\n- [ ] release-notes.json\n\n**产出:**\n每个服务有规范的\nCommit 和 Changelog","x":100,"y":100,"width":350,"height":280,"color":"3"},
					{"id":"roadmap_week1","type":"text","text":"### 🚀 Week 1 快速启动\n\n**Day 1-2: Commits 规范**\n- [ ] 创建 `.commitlintrc.json`\n- [ ] 配置 CI job\n- [ ] 编写规范文档\n\n**Day 3-4: Linear 配置**\n- [ ] 注册团队账户\n- [ ] GitLab 集成\n- [ ] 导入现有 Issues\n\n**Day 5: 验证**\n- [ ] 完整流程测试","x":2100,"y":100,"width":550,"height":280,"color":"1"},
					{"id":"roadmap_goals","type":"text","text":"### 🎯 最终目标\n\n**可见性:**\n- leader能看到每次变更内容\n- 产品能追踪需求交付状态\n- 开发能快速定位问题来源\n\n**可靠性:**\n- 自动化测试门禁\n- 可控的环境晋升\n- 一键回滚能力\n\n**效率:**\n- 需求→交付全自动化\n- 减少沟通成本\n- 缩短交付周期","x":2700,"y":100,"width":450,"height":400,"color":"4"},
