		{"id":"054323e73a6888da","type":"group","x":3500,"y":-1460,"width":420,"height":534},
		{"id":"flow_main","type":"text","text":"### 🔄 核心流程\n\n```\nIdea → Issue → Branch\n  ↓\nCode → Test → Review\n  ↓  \nMerge → Build → Push\n  ↓\nKargo → ArgoCD → Deploy\n  ↓\nMonitor → Feedback → Iterate\n```\n\n贯彻[[声明式 和 推送式 思想]]的声明式：\n- 继承k8s的实现思路，用声明式的方式watch环境\n\t- watch main分支\n\t- watch 镜像仓库\n\t- watch gitops的yaml配置仓库","x":3957,"y":-1450,"width":400,"height":524,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"ci_notify","type":"text","text":"### 5️⃣ Notify\n\n- Slack/飞书/钉钉 通知\n- 变更内容摘要\n- 关联 Issue 列表\n- 部署状态更新","x":2460,"y":-1140,"width":400,"height":184,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"ci_publish","type":"text","text":"### 4️⃣ Publish\n\n- 生成 CHANGELOG.md\n- 提取关联 Issue IDs\n- 创建 release-notes.json\n- 版本号: `v1.2.3-abc1234`","x":2000,"y":-1140,"width":400,"height":184,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"7d8e72c752e1aeeb","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2026/生产环境 预发环境 镜像变更操作手册.md","x":4648,"y":-1379,"width":786,"height":478},
		{"id":"ci_validate","type":"text","text":"### 1️⃣ Validate\n\n- Code Lint\n  - golangci-lint\n  - ruff (Python)\n- Commit Lint\n  - conventional","x":2000,"y":-1450,"width":260,"height":230,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ci_build","type":"text","text":"### 3️⃣ Build\n\n- Docker Build\n- Multi-stage\n- Layer Cache\n- Push Registry","x":2600,"y":-1450,"width":260,"height":230,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"fcceb599bb77bba1","type":"file","file":"📥 Inbox/gitops 仓库 结构设计.md","x":4040,"y":-1920,"width":400,"height":288},
		{"id":"26a4bfa92c8e746e","type":"file","file":"Atlas/Canvas/压测环境 自动变更流水线.canvas","x":4653,"y":-1898,"width":400,"height":400},
		{"id":"ci_test","type":"text","text":"### 2️⃣ Test\n\n- 单元测试\n- 集成测试\n- 覆盖率报告\n- Cobertura","x":2300,"y":-1450,"width":260,"height":230,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"gitops_argocd","type":"text","text":"### 🐙 ArgoCD\n**GitOps 同步引擎**\n\n- Watch GitOps Repo\n- 自动 Sync 到 K8s\n- 漂移检测 & 自愈\n- 回滚支持","x":3100,"y":-1182,"width":380,"height":256,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"mdu_title","type":"text","text":"## Minimum Deployable Unit\n三位一体变更单元","x":0,"y":-1450,"width":700,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"env_staging","type":"text","text":"### 🧪 Staging (AWS)\n\n**触发**: Main Branch Merge → 自动  \n**用途**: 集成验证 & UAT  \n**验证**: 集成测试 + E2E  \n**运行时间**: ≥ 2小时无告警","x":700,"y":-720,"width":400,"height":190,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"mdu_migration","type":"text","text":"### 🗄️ Database Schema Migration\n\n| 语言 | 工具 | 特点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Golang | golang-migrate / Atlas | 轻量/声明式 |\n| Python | Alembic | SQLAlchemy生态 |","x":0,"y":-1145,"width":680,"height":190,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"mdu_config","type":"text","text":"### ⚙️ ConfigMap/Secrets\n\n- 环境变量配置\n- 版本: `Git Commit Hash`\n- 管理: Kustomize overlay","x":360,"y":-1350,"width":320,"height":150,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b9d120efe376be31","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2026/CICD 简易流程.md","x":5273,"y":-1920,"width":781,"height":467},
		{"id":"mdu_image","type":"text","text":"### 📦 Container Image\n\n- OCI Artifact\n- 版本: `SemVer + Git SHA`\n- 存储: Container Registry","x":0,"y":-1350,"width":320,"height":150,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"env_local","type":"text","text":"### 🏠 Local Cluster\n\n**触发**: Feature Branch Push  \n**用途**: 开发调试  \n**验证**: 单元测试  \n**工具**: k3d / kind","x":0,"y":-720,"width":350,"height":190,"color":"5"},
		{
			"id":"gitops_terraform",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 🏗️ Terraform\n**AWS 基础设施即代码**\n\n- EKS 集群管理\n- RDS/ElastiCache\n- VPC/Security Groups\n- IAM Roles",
			"styleAttributes":{"border":"dashed"},
			"x":3520,
			"y":-1182,
			"width":380,
			"height":226,
			"color":"5"
		},
		{"id":"dev_tools","type":"text","text":"### 🛠️ 开发工具推荐\n\n| 工具 | 用途 | 场景 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Tilt** | 本地K8s开发自动化 | 多服务开发 |\n| **Telepresence** | 注入远程集群 | 访问远程资源 |\n| **Skaffold** | 开发工作流 | CI/CD本地模拟 |","x":1000,"y":-1145,"width":750,"height":190,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"dev_k8s","type":"text","text":"### ☸️ 本地K8s集群\n\n**集群选择:**\n- k3d (推荐)\n- kind\n- minikube\n\n**完整依赖上下文:**\n其他微服务、DB、MQ、Cache","x":1400,"y":-1450,"width":350,"height":283,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"dev_local","type":"text","text":"### 🖥️ 本地开发环境\n\n- IDE / 编辑器\n- 代码编写\n- 单元测试\n- 热重载调试\n\n```\ngo test ./...\npytest tests/\n```","x":1000,"y":-1450,"width":350,"height":283,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"gitops_repo","type":"text","text":"### 📁 GitOps Repo\n**Kustomize 配置管理**\n\n```\ngitops-repo/\n├── base/\n│   └── deployment.yaml\n├── overlays/\n│   ├── staging/\n│   └── production/\n└── kustomization.yaml\n```","x":3520,"y":-1450,"width":380,"height":250,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"e979ad33ab03f5f4","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2025/公司 117集群的argocd.md","x":3560,"y":-1920,"width":400,"height":288},
		{"id":"b28b87d7eb6d2948","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2026/公司 117集群的 kargo.md","x":3100,"y":-1920,"width":400,"height":288},
		{"id":"gitops_kargo","type":"text","text":"### 🚢 Kargo\n**镜像版本监控 & 晋升管理**\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: kargo.akuity.io/v1alpha1\nkind: Stage\nspec:\n  subscriptions:\n    warehouse: images\n  promotionMechanisms:\n    gitRepoUpdates: [...]\n```","x":3100,"y":-1450,"width":380,"height":250,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"bd7492bf0c897d43","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2026/k8s 本地开发联调的工具 - skaffold.md","x":1515,"y":-2045,"width":400,"height":347},
		{"id":"cdb7f170cfd5aefe","type":"text","text":"## 从需求到生产：GitOps驱动的端到端交付体系\n\n![[端到端可靠交付蓝图.png]]","x":-1212,"y":-1575,"width":917,"height":569,"color":"1"},
		{
			"id":"d7979f80c608ea7c",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## 横向维度： 单服务全生命周期\n- 代码->上线 - 循环\n\t- 最小可部署单元\n\t- 开发阶段就上k8s，保证配置一致性。\n\t- GitOps 具体使用 \n## 纵向维度： 需求到交付闭环\n- 需求 kanban - 循环\n\t- 需求 -> issue\n\t- commit 和issue \n\t- 交付上线通知\n\t- issue 自动close \n\n## ai agent 使用\n- vibe kanban - 循环\n\t- 需求，补充上下文和工具\n\t- deepresearch & plan mode\n\t- 执行并review后合入 \n",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-1183,
			"y":-878,
			"width":751,
			"height":603
		},
