		{"id":"tools_list","type":"text","text":"### 🛠️ 技术栈清单\n\n**需求管理**\n- Linear ⭐ (推荐)\n- GitLab Issues ✅\n\n**代码托管 & CI/CD**\n- GitLab ✅\n- GitLab CI ✅\n- GitLab Registry ✅\n\n**GitOps**\n- ArgoCD ✅\n- Kargo ✅\n- Kustomize ✅\n\n**基础设施**\n- Terraform ✅\n- Kubernetes (AWS EKS) ✅\n\n**服务网格 & 渐进交付**\n- Istio\n- Argo Rollouts\n\n**数据库迁移**\n- golang-migrate (Go)\n- Alembic (Python)\n\n**Changelog**\n- conventional-changelog\n\n**本地开发**\n- k3d / Tilt ✅","x":3900,"y":150,"width":550,"height":700,"color":"5"},
