		{"id":"changelog_single","type":"text","text":"### 📄 单服务 Changelog\n\n每个服务 Tag 时自动生成:\n\n```json\n// release-notes.json\n{\n  \"service\": \"user-service\",\n  \"version\": \"v1.2.3\",\n  \"date\": \"2024-01-15\",\n  \"changelog\": \"...\",\n  \"related_issues\": [\"ENG-123\"]\n}\n```","x":2600,"y":150,"width":500,"height":200,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"changelog_output","type":"text","text":"### 📋 聚合 Changelog 示例\n\n```markdown\n# Platform Release v2024.01.15\n\n## ✨ New Features\n- **[user-service]** OAuth2 登录支持 (ENG-123)\n- **[order-service]** Apple Pay 支付 (ENG-789)\n\n## 🐛 Bug Fixes  \n- **[user-service]** 修复头像上传问题 (ENG-456)\n\n## 📦 Services Updated\n| Service | From | To |\n|---------|------|-----|\n| user-service | v1.2.2 | v1.2.3 |\n| order-service | v2.0.0 | v2.0.1 |\n```","x":2600,"y":380,"width":500,"height":280,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"8c36f541a4879a46","type":"file","file":"Extras/Attachments/vibe coding 看板.png","x":1036,"y":1458,"width":1629,"height":692},
		{"id":"cfd5e558ccdebca3","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2026/我的 ai agent 流水线.md","x":578,"y":1469,"width":400,"height":670},
		{"id":"1f0857bc4ecbd6e7","type":"file","file":"📥 Inbox/claude code 周边神器.md","x":4101,"y":1522,"width":400,"height":566},
		{"id":"req_epic","type":"text","text":"### 📦 Epic\n**业务需求**\n\n- 大型业务目标\n- 跨团队协作\n- 季度/年度规划\n\n`ENG-1`","x":0,"y":260,"width":260,"height":180,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"changelog_aggregator","type":"text","text":"### 🔄 Release Aggregator\n\n```\nplatform-releases/\n├── scripts/\n│   ├── aggregate.py\n│   └── notify.py\n├── manifests/\n│   └── 2024/01/\n└── changelogs/\n    └── 2024/01/\n```\n\n聚合 20 个服务的变更","x":3150,"y":150,"width":450,"height":200,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"commit_link","type":"text","text":"### 🔗 双向链接实现\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  Linear Issue (ENG-123)  ◀───────────▶  GitLab Commit/MR       │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  正向: Issue → 查看关联的 Commits/MRs → 代码变更详情               │\n│  反向: Commit → 查看关联的 Issues → 原始需求/Bug描述              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```","x":1280,"y":150,"width":1020,"height":251,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"commit_types","type":"text","text":"### 🏷️ Type 类型定义 举例\n\n| Type | 说明 | SemVer |\n|------|------|--------|\n| `feat` | ✨ 新功能 | MINOR |\n| `fix` | 🐛 Bug修复 | PATCH |\n| `perf` | ⚡ 性能优化 | PATCH |\n| `refactor` | 🔨 重构 | - |\n| `docs` | 📝 文档 | - |\n| `breaking` | 💥 破坏性 | MAJOR |","x":1850,"y":440,"width":450,"height":220,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"0e765ee6ac1c3d4b","type":"file","file":"temps/2026-01-22 变更 changelog 现状.md","x":3160,"y":380,"width":440,"height":280},
		{"id":"da740ae30542a5af","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2026/gitlab issue 和commit双向关联.md","x":1280,"y":440,"width":500,"height":455},
		{"id":"commit_keywords","type":"text","text":"### 🔑 关联关键词\n\n**自动关闭 Issue:**\n- `Closes: ENG-123`\n- `Fixes: ENG-123`\n- `Resolves: ENG-123`\n\n**引用关联:**\n- `Related: ENG-12`\n- `Refs: ENG-456`\n- `See: ENG-789`","x":1850,"y":678,"width":450,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"11fbcbc56bd50de4","type":"file","file":"📥 Inbox/moc - skills 推荐列表.md","x":2822,"y":1522,"width":484,"height":566},
		{"id":"env_rollout","type":"text","text":"### 🎚️ 发布策略\n\n| 策略 | 场景 | 实现 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Rolling | 日常发布 | K8s Deployment |\n| Blue-Green | 快速回滚 | Argo Rollouts |\n| Canary | 渐进验证 | Argo Rollouts + Istio |\n| 全链路灰度 | A/B测试 | Istio VirtualService |","x":2930,"y":-766,"width":550,"height":346,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"env_gates","type":"text","text":"### 🚦 Quality Gates (晋升条件)\n\n- ✅ 所有自动化测试通过\n- ✅ Staging 运行 ≥2h 无告警\n- ✅ 错误率 < 0.1%, P99延迟 < 500ms\n- ✅ 至少一名 Reviewer 审批","x":2200,"y":-720,"width":500,"height":254,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"env_prod","type":"text","text":"### 🚀 Production (AWS)\n\n**触发**: 手动审批  \n**用途**: 生产环境  \n**验证**: 质量门禁通过  \n**回滚**: ArgoCD一键回滚","x":1450,"y":-720,"width":400,"height":160,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"req_bug","type":"text","text":"### 🐛 Bug\n**缺陷单**\n\n- 问题追踪\n- 严重等级\n- 复现步骤\n\n`ENG-456`","x":900,"y":260,"width":250,"height":180,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"req_task","type":"text","text":"### ✅ Task\n**技术任务**\n\n- 具体开发任务\n- 1-3天工作量\n- 可分配给个人\n\n`ENG-123`","x":600,"y":260,"width":260,"height":180,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"req_alternatives","type":"text","text":"### 📊 工具对比\n\n| 工具 | GitLab集成 | 适合规模 | 推荐 |\n|------|------------|----------|------|\n| **Linear** | ✅ 原生 | 5-50人 | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| GitLab Issues | ✅ 原生 | 任意 | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| Jira | ✅ 插件 | 50+人 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| Notion | ⚠️ 有限 | 5-20人 | ⭐⭐⭐ |","x":600,"y":480,"width":550,"height":200,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"req_title","type":"text","text":"## 🎯 需求分层结构\n**业务需求 → 产品需求 → 技术任务 → Bug单**","x":0,"y":150,"width":1150,"height":80,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"req_status","type":"text","text":"### 🔄 Issue 状态自动流转\n\n`Backlog` → `Todo` → `In Progress` (Branch Created) → `In Review` (MR Created) → `Done` (MR Merged) → `Deployed` (ArgoCD Sync)","x":0,"y":720,"width":1150,"height":120,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"req_feature","type":"text","text":"### 🎁 Feature\n**产品需求**\n\n- 可交付的功能\n- Sprint规划\n- 用户故事\n\n`ENG-12`","x":300,"y":260,"width":260,"height":180,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"req_linear","type":"text","text":"### 🎯 推荐工具: Linear\n\n**为什么选择 Linear:**\n- ✅ 现代化 UI，键盘优先\n- ✅ 原生 GitLab 集成\n- ✅ 自动状态流转\n- ✅ 内置 Cycle Analytics\n- ✅ 10人团队 ~$80/月\n\n[linear.app](https://linear.app)","x":0,"y":480,"width":550,"height":200,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"c8dc3a263758326a","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2026/灰度发布 Argo Rollouts.md","x":3557,"y":-760,"width":400,"height":440},
		{"id":"4f7e7ecffdbfe86a","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2025/团队git工作流和分支管理.md","x":1730,"y":-170,"width":470,"height":170},
		{"id":"changelog_notify","type":"text","text":"### 📢 通知渠道\n\n| 渠道 | 用途 | 时机 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Slack/飞书** | 即时通知 | 每次部署完成 |\n| **Email** | 周报/汇总 | 每周一上午 |\n| **Linear** | Issue状态更新 | MR Merge / Deploy |\n| **GitLab** | Release Note | Tag 创建 |","x":2600,"y":700,"width":1000,"height":178,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"9a7251dc94786108","type":"file","file":"temps/crawler 爬虫仓库为例 - 讲解 lint test build api-test.md","x":730,"y":-170,"width":400,"height":170},
